net.minecraft.data.DataProvider
public abstract class TagProviderBase<T> extends net.minecraft.data.tags.IntrinsicHolderTagsProvider<T>
A provider for tags of a type. If you want to use block, item or fluid tags, use CommonTagsProviderBase. You can set your tags in setup. With defaultTags(Object), you can add default tags that can be retrieved from the element.
